"overview" : "Suraj Limited is engaged in the manufacturing of stainless steel, pipes tubes, U-tubes, and flanges and fittings. The Company offers its products in a range of categories, such as instrumentation tubes, seamless heat exchanger tubes, seamless heat exchanger U-tubes, seamless pipes, stainless steel flanges and seamless buttweld fitting. Its stainless steel instrumentation tubes have various applications, such as heat exchangers, instrumentation, hydraulic and pneumatic system, nuclear power plants, automotive industries and pharmaceutical. It also manufactures a range of austenitic, ferritic, martensitic, duplex and super duplex heat exchanger tubes. Its heat exchanger tubes are used for the cooling, heating or re-heating of fluids, gases, and air in a range of industries, such as fabrication of shell and tube heat exchangers, and oil refineries and petrochemicals. Its heat exchanger U-tubes and pipes are used in oil and gas, fertilizer, power plant and other industries."
